name: geeet
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "geeet" %}
{% set version = "0.1.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b9ea0652338ae85c4352790768fc52c7d55bf3784bc89aad42bc466a450cc571

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - numpy
    - python >=3.7

test:
  imports:
    - geeet

about:
  home: https://github.com/kaust-halo/geeet
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Evapotranspiration (ET) models for use in python and with integration into Google Earth Engine.
  doc_url: https://kaust-halo.github.io/geeet
  dev_url: https://github.com/kaust-halo/geeet

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - lopezvoliver
